w.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/T%E1%BB%8Bch-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-h%E1%BB%AFu-t%E1%BA%B7ng/poem-_7CqmIso_KPrgdZzKRq2pw">Tịch thượng hữu tặng - 席上有贈</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/author-wyu82iSv-bH9msUkq5vWDQ">Hàn Ốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%C3%ADch-Ng%C3%B4-S%E1%BB%9F-l%C6%B0u-bi%E1%BB%87t-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n-l%C6%B0u-h%E1%BA%ADu-ki%C3%AAm-m%E1%BA%A1c-ph%E1%BB%A7-ch%C6%B0-c%C3%B4ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-li%E1%BB%85u-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-VusrYuqrkvq24lkjJ2HUYQ">Tương thích Ngô Sở, lưu biệt Chương sứ quân lưu hậu kiêm mạc phủ chư công, đắc liễu tự - 將適吳楚，留別章使君留後兼幕府諸公，得柳字</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-L%C3%BD/U%E1%BB%B7-gia-n%E1%BB%99i/poem-1Wai90NIRez-REzjhCaucg">Uỷ gia nội - 慰家內</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-L%C3%BD/author-25FyZ6rpi0e-evNzYaWVZQ">Nguyễn Văn Lý</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy-Trinh/Xu%C3%A2n-ba-kh%C3%BAc/poem-SKJB6ZzS3TBp8D1Ybr6h8g">Xuân ba khúc - 春波曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy-Trinh/author-tbuJ74IPkvZZ32WHu1yvJw">Dương Duy Trinh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
